@page "/" 
@inject NavigationManager Navigation

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100 bg-body-tertiary">
    <div class="card col-12 row-6 col-md-6 row-md-6 shadow no-border-radius" style="max-width: 500px">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="logo mb-4"></div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold">로그인</h5>
            <p class="text-secondary">CoffeeTime에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</p>
            <div class="alert alert-warning py-2 no-border-radius mb-5">
                <i class="bi bi-exclamation-lg me-1"></i>
                CloudInteractive ID로 로그인해야 합니다.
            </div>
            <a class="btn btn-primary w-100 no-border-radius py-2" href="/oauth/signin">
                <i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i>
                클라우드인터렉티브 통합인증
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
